Sqoot,is,a,service,that,aggregates,the,web,s,daily,deals,in,a,single,place,and,provides,tools,for,users,to,display,the,deals,on,their,sites,The,Sqoot,API,exposes,thousands,of,deals,and,allows,developers,to,make,RESTful,requests,and,receive,offers,back,in,JSON,format,Users,can,filter,offers,by,category,and,location,by,supplying,parameters,in,the,query,string